Author: thefakemexoxo
Text: I wanted to try the new nacho crunch double stack taco because my boyfriend said the chipotle one was good. I was committed to the 310 calories if it was good. But it was so dry and awful that I just couldn’t bare the thought of wasting calories on it. So I came home and purged like... 1/4 of it. It was only like 15 minutes and somehow that’s all that would come up. Eventually all I got was phlegm :(

Author: mamapajamarolled
Text: TBQH one of the best cuisines to purge, and for 10$ you can really fuck some shit up. Shitty burrito gang ASSEMBLE!
